wikipedia_page.main: Stephen Sean Eskinazi (born 28 March 1994) is a South African born, Australian raised, professional cricketer who plays primarily for Middlesex County Cricket Club in England. He is a dual citizen of Australia and the United Kingdom and is a right-handed batsman who also keeps wicket.
